main event: Several persons observed a round saucer-shaped object the size of a small automobile in Elkton, Kentucky on November 10, 1957.
interesting points: The object was seen for approximately 15 minutes before it disappeared.,Witnesses speculated that it could be a Military or Civilian Aircraft.,The object was round and saucer-shaped.,The sighting occurred during the late evening (029 hours).,There were multiple witnesses to the sighting.
